{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Exovoid Carnage</strong> is an intense <strong>WAVE-BASED ARENA SHOOTER</strong> that cranks up the chaos to eleven! <strong>SHOOT! SHRED! SURVIVE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102800/extras/GetInThere.gif?t=1728060478\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019re dropped onto the colossal Leviathan Station, an alien fortress the size of a planet. Armed with only a gun and no time to lose, you\u2019re launched into a relentless fight for survival. Battle through <u>waves</u> of vicious aliens, blast your way to victory, and get catapulted to the next room!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102800/extras/highresscreenshot00041_720.png?t=1728060478\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Equip game-changing power-ups like <strong>Rapid Fire</strong>, <strong>Double Damage</strong>, and the devastating <strong>Saw-blade Tornado</strong>.  As you progress, the enemies get fiercer, but so do you. Every death means a new chance to try again with advantages based on your previous run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102800/extras/HighresScreenshot00044.png?t=1728060478\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How far can you go? Sharpen your skills, beat your high score, and see if you have what it takes to survive EXOVOID CARNAGE!</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3102800?t=1728060478","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102800/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1728060478","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102800/776c8f565bad